flowchart TD
    Start([Revision de compliance]) --> CaptchaCheck{Requiere bypass CAPTCHA?}
    CaptchaCheck -->|Si| BLOCKED[MANUAL_ASSISTED - CRITICAL]
    CaptchaCheck -->|No| AntiBotCheck{Requiere evasion anti-bot?}
    AntiBotCheck -->|Si| BLOCKED
    AntiBotCheck -->|No| RateLimitCheck{Requiere evasion rate limit?}
    RateLimitCheck -->|Si| BLOCKED
    RateLimitCheck -->|No| AuthBypassCheck{Requiere bypass auth?}
    AuthBypassCheck -->|Si| BLOCKED
    AuthBypassCheck -->|No| ApiCheck{Tiene API oficial + docs + ToS?}
    ApiCheck -->|Si| OFFICIAL[OFFICIAL_API - Riesgo LOW]
    ApiCheck -->|No| AuthIntCheck{Integracion autorizada + ToS?}
    AuthIntCheck -->|Si| AUTHORIZED[AUTHORIZED_INTEGRATION - Riesgo MEDIUM]
    AuthIntCheck -->|No| MANUAL[MANUAL_ASSISTED - Riesgo HIGH]
